<!-- Banner -->
<div class="banner-peetayers" style="background-image: linear-gradient(-225deg, rgba(0,101,168,0.6) 0%, rgba(0,36,61,0.6) 50%), url('<%=image_path "https://source.unsplash.com/collection/865018/1000x300"%>');">
  <div class="banner-peetayers-content">
    <h1>Welcome</h1>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- End Banner -->

<div class="container">
  <div class="body">
    <div class="row">

      <div class="column-1">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-3">
          <div class="polaroid flo">
            <div class="polaroid-img" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.2)), url('<%=image_path "peetayers/romain.jpg" %>');">
            </div>
            <p class="polaroid-text"><strong>Romain, 28 ans<strong></p>
            <p class="polaroid-desc">"I'll be happy to help you!"</p>
          </div>
          <br>

          <div class="infos">
            <div class="infos-title text-center">
              <p><strong>Information checked</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="infos-content">
              <ul><p><i class="far fa-check-circle"></i> Official ID</p></ul>
              <ul><p><i class="far fa-check-circle"></i> Phone</p></ul>
              <ul><p><i class="far fa-check-circle"></i> Email</p></ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="column-2">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-9">

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space1 text-center">
                <div class="space1-title">
                  <h3>Hello, I'm Romain!</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="space1-content">
                  <p>Montreal, Canada ° since 2 months</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Available services</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <div class="row">
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/suitcase.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Prepare your trip</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/location.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Housing services</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/medical-history.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Help with admins</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/chat.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Speak local</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/cheers.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Local tips</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Languages?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>French, English & Spanish</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Why do you like Montreal?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>Culture, accès, proximité, accueil, outdoor sports.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Your favorite spots in Montreal?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>L’abreuvoir, siboire, 3 brasseurs.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Why do you want to become a Peetayer?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>I would like to become a Peetayer to help anybody that need my advices or my help when they want to live in Canada and specially in Montreal. When I moved to London 4 years ago then in Montreal 2 month ago I was very happy to get the help from friends who already live there to answer my questions before to come and in the first few days of arrivals.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>What are your interests?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>Basket-ball, Running and ski , All music style (except metal music)</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>What about Romain?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>I am Romain I am 29 years old (defenitely less in my head). I am passionnate by sports and fashion. I like the outdoor activities as Ski, trekking, trail-running. I achieved my first trail race last summer in Chamonix (42 km and 3000+) the best experience in my life so far! My passion is the retail (reason of my job) but also basket-ball (I play since 20 years). I like to speak with friends and people and share personnal experiences (you become richer when you have great people around yourself). I am fiancee to Noemie who become Helicopter Pilot in Montreal. We are both coming from the Alps (between La Clusaz and Chamonix). People say I am nice with everybody welcome anyone and always in good mood with the smile on my face, an easy going person with lot of motivations.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Which countries have you visited?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>Uk to work, Italy holidays, Tunisia holidays, Holland to work, germany to work, belgium to work, sweden to work, switzerland to work</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

